assertion: I find nothing more relaxing than making scented candles.
I once went skinny dipping with Sharon from EastEnders.
She once booked me a stripper and it went so badly that I spend the rest of the night trying to cheer him up.
She once asked me to pop into her house to get rid of a spider. Ten minutes later, she asked me to leave because I was making matters worse.
I once accidentally left a goldfish on top of a petrol pump.
I found out my girlfriend was cheating on me while I was bouncing on a trampoline and spotted her over the fence with another man.
